{"tid":1776649,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳小春提議把弟弟送人吧...最後弟弟也真的以三千元港幣被賣掉","createTime":"2019-12-09T16:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T16:53:58.000Z","uid":135077,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa97807ead277d4bed6e8c3959ff4ed1499a491","tid":1776649,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"前惠州政協陳小春在台北開演唱會，遭網民口誅筆伐，表演場外更被噴漆「強姦犯陳小春」等字句──我fact-check過，陳小春應該不是強姦犯，他只是十四歲時非禮未成年少女，罪名成立，留了案底而已（這段juicy的黑歷史，見於大陸網站轉載的〈香港藝人犯事記錄大盤點〉）。關於陳小春，有個問題困擾我很多年：以他的長相才藝，憑什麼能夠走紅？<br />\n<br />\n第一次認識陳小春，是一九九四年看《金枝玉葉》，印象很深，不因為他演得好，只覺得他混在一群俊男美女之中，倍感篤眼篤鼻。《古惑仔》系列我一向不喜歡，但平心而論，他演「山雞」這類囂張無腦角色是恰如其分的，因為他只是做自己。<br />\n<br />\n時來運到，山雞也開始裝出鳳凰的樣子了，就像今天的中國。香港回歸後一年，無綫重拍《鹿鼎記》，居然由他演韋小寶，未開鏡已註定失敗。有梁朝偉、周星馳珠玉在前，陳小春除了像黎耀祥一樣有股化不開的太監味之外，何德何能演機靈的韋爵爺呢？這版本的《鹿鼎記》該是金庸改編劇中最爛之一，但無論如何未夠班，陳小春還是「上位」了，就像當年的董建華。<br />\n<br />\n陳小春高調「愛國」之前，我對他也無好感。外形不算討好，歌唱得不動聽，做諧星欠喜感，當小生又太醜，除了演小混混入型入格，根本乏善足陳。翻查他的過去更得人驚：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除了非禮，陳小春小時候在大陸生活，家境貧困，竟跟父母提議：「不如把弟弟送人吧。」當下遭到父母毒打，但最後弟弟也真的以三千元港幣被賣掉。憶述此事時，陳小春自言家裏太窮，「怕弟弟過得太辛苦」──作惡也大條道理，跟香港警察臭味相投，也難怪他撐警了。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n小時為錢賣弟，少年好色非禮，中年後走個狗屎運，趕上香港最後一班順風車，從此水鬼升城隍，一朝得志語無倫次。陳小春的成功路，恰巧倒映出香港的衰亡史──不是社會賢達都變成人渣，而是人渣都被捧為賢達了。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191209/20821461/?fbclid=IwAR1sdDB0k2NyAyr44DiBAWc9AztFQP8SR21_jw0PzRkZezWh5kr_86lDViE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191209%2F20821461%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1sdDB0k2NyAyr44DiBAWc9AztFQP8SR21_jw0PzRkZezWh5kr_86lDViE&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0zob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=2d728885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191209%2F20821461%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1sdDB0k2NyAyr44DiBAWc9AztFQP8SR21_jw0PzRkZezWh5kr_86lDViE&h=f1da719c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191209/20821461/?fbclid=IwAR1sdDB0k2NyAyr44DiBAWc9AztFQP8SR21_jw0PzRkZezWh5kr_86lDViE</a>"},{"pid":"bc3312b4398c09ab5cfea0a52815756bdb07f969","tid":1776649,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a786a17e306ca2cef59b4b8402ae4f6fa4bef82","tid":1776649,"uid":127553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6195583f7288261507181347bf46bbb29db6cde","tid":1776649,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"只是非禮，不是強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7eb812ef1556a058e72e55e88c4734bde4da4c","tid":1776649,"uid":170987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"「作惡也大條道理，跟香港警察臭味相投，也難怪他撐警了」"},{"pid":"d11e19f42079485ab07b955a93c5fd6dec85af03","tid":1776649,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"Double fact check, source: <a href=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/celebrity/Jordan-Chan-childhood?fbclid=IwAR1ksBmkVJMuMn6rLiib6chd-jWtf0OjxRi7LJn30F404GV_rJz3XscguAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fcelebrity%2FJordan-Chan-childhood%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ksBmkVJMuMn6rLiib6chd-jWtf0OjxRi7LJn30F404GV_rJz3XscguAA&d=qnVsOlg